text: Positive results with tap water show rapid Covid tests inaccurate
Tap water is testing positive for COVID!
Video shows tap water tested positive for Covid-19
entity_strings: tap water, tested positive for Covid

text: Tap water can return a positive lateral flow test result for Covid-19.
A post shared on Facebook claims a BinaxNOW rapid home COVID-19 test turning positive when exposed to water shows the coronavirus is in drinking water.
